---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="reading" description="What I read, what landed, and why the gap tells you something.">
  <header class="animate-fade-up" style="margin-bottom: 40px;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.025em;">reading</h1>
    <p class="text-dim" style="margin-top: 12px; font-size: 17px;">weekly digests. not summaries — filters. what landed, what didn't, and what that says about where the signal actually sits.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="animate-fade-up delay-1" style="margin-bottom: 32px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;">
    <div>
      <a href="/reading/books" class="font-mono text-sm no-underline hover:text-accent text-accent">→ books for programmers</a>
      <span class="text-faint text-sm ml-2">— a reading list for junior devs</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <a href="/reading/library" class="font-mono text-sm no-underline hover:text-accent text-accent">→ library</a>
      <span class="text-faint text-sm ml-2">— curated across strategy, systems, leadership & startups</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="animate-fade-up delay-2" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 32px; margin-top: 40px;">
    <a href="/reading/week-14" class="block no-underline group">
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: baseline; margin-bottom: 6px;">
        <span class="font-mono text-faint" style="font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.08em;">2026.04.06</span>
        <span class="font-mono text-faint" style="font-size: 11px;">week 14</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="group-hover:text-accent transition-colors" style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 8px;">two reads and a pipeline that won't shut up</h3>
      <p class="text-dim" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65;">13% read rate. lowest ever. saved 11 things, read 2. the system kept feeding me while i wasn't eating.</p>
    </a>

    <a href="/reading/week-13" class="block no-underline group">
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: baseline; margin-bottom: 6px;">
        <span class="font-mono text-faint" style="font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.08em;">2026.03.28</span>
        <span class="font-mono text-faint" style="font-size: 11px;">week 13</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="group-hover:text-accent transition-colors" style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 8px;">three ben thompson pieces and one surprise</h3>
      <p class="text-dim" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65;">the stratechery streak continued. then a journalist built an iOS app with claude code and made me think harder than any of ben's frameworks.</p>
    </a>

    <a href="/reading/week-12" class="block no-underline group">
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: baseline; margin-bottom: 6px;">
        <span class="font-mono text-faint" style="font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.08em;">2026.03.20</span>
        <span class="font-mono text-faint" style="font-size: 11px;">week 12</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="group-hover:text-accent transition-colors" style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 8px;">the ratio is usually like this</h3>
      <p class="text-dim" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65;">four reads on ai tooling. one validated what already works. one taught something that was already figured out. one actually changed a workflow.</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</Layout>
